            <title>[LU-13064] Check permissions when accessing changelogs</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-13064</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;root permissions should be checked when reading or clearing changelogs from clients. In particular, if root is squashed via a nodemap entry, it should not be allowed to access changelogs.&lt;/p&gt;

